title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
